This add-on will allow you to use JUI Accordion.

Installation:
    Check readme file of ds-addons pack.

Dependencies:
	jQuery UI

Usage:
	Use it in Page like this:

	Example:
        $ac = $b->add('Accordion/View_Accordion');
        
        $ac->addTab('First one', 'foo')
            ->add('View_Warning')->set('First content here');
        $ac->addTab('Second one', 'bar')
            ->add('View_Info')->set('Second content');
        
        $ac->addTabURL('qwerty', 'Ajax one'); // remotely load page index/qwerty

Known problems:
    none
    
Author:
	Imants Horsts
